<p>name is on the Boat Roll of the Kildonan Castle to sail in about a week.  Walked aroun Warminster with Bill &amp; Pat &amp; had tea at Y.M. Manorhouse in Sutton Veny.  A decent meal 5/- for the 3 of us.</p>
<p>Monday 17th</p>
<p>Bill left this morning by the Passies.</p>
<p>Tuesday 18th</p>
<p>A good deal of paraide work going through Q.M. etc.  Pat B. &amp; I went into Warminster &amp; made some purchases for the voyage.</p>
